# This copy exists because examples/nvfs is a separate git submodule and
# cannot directly import from src/os/crypto/ (cross-submodule imports are
# not resolvable — confirmed in .sstack/spostgre-nvfs-storage/state.md,
# bench pass_todo note: "examples.nvfs.src.core.arena.* not resolvable from
# main-repo bench/ runner (separate git submodule)").
